				<outline text="Personal Democracy Forum" created="Thu, 22 Mar 2007 22:04:10 GMT">
					<outline text="I spoke with &lt;a href=&quot;http://micah.sifry.com/&quot;&gt;Micah Sifry&lt;/a&gt; this afternoon and we agreed that I would do a keynote at the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.personaldemocracy.com/&quot;&gt;Personal Democracy Forum&lt;/a&gt; in New York, on &lt;a href=&quot;http://pdf2007.confabb.com/conferences/PDF2007/details&quot;&gt;May 18&lt;/a&gt; at Pace University. " created="Thu, 22 Mar 2007 22:04:19 GMT"/>
