				<outline text="Programming at newspapers">
					<outline text="If I were younger, I'd jump at this &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.holovaty.com/blog/archive/2007/03/08/2108&quot;&gt;job&lt;/a&gt; at the Washington Post. " created="Sat, 10 Mar 2007 15:02:52 GMT"/>
