					<outline text="All the software I wanted when I was younger was about writing and reading news, it turns out, although I doubt if I could have explained this then. " created="Sat, 10 Mar 2007 15:04:15 GMT"/>
					<outline text="So if you're a tech hottie who reads this blog and says &lt;i&gt;Yeah!&lt;/i&gt; out loud to what you read here, I'd say it's a good bet you'd fit in as a programmer in a news room, so go for it." created="Sat, 10 Mar 2007 15:04:54 GMT"/>
